{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"TextDecoderStream.fatal","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/fatal","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API\">Encoding API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/encoding\"><code>encoding</code></a></li><li><em><code>fatal</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/ignoreBOM\"><code>ignoreBOM</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/readable\"><code>readable</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream/writable\"><code>writable</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Encoding API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>fatal</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a> interface is a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>boolean</code></a> indicating if the error mode of the <code>TextDecoderStream</code> object is set to <code>fatal</code>.</p>\n<p>The two possible values of error mod